title: Aureal - The podcast platform that pays you

creator: TitanDLT IT solutions
descriptionHtml:
Aureal is the easiest way to monetise your podcast without ads or sponsorships. It's a podcast app with works like reddit.

Now you can create, connect, distribute, go live, curate and most importantly monetise your podcast hassle-free. Finding sponsors and ads has become a thing in the past.

--- A Decentralized Reward Engine.
Aureal is built on top of HIVE, a social blockchain which rewards its community members for their contribution. Here you'll earn Hive tokens for every interaction you do on the app. and once you connect your podcast, you start monetising right from day one, no matter who you are or where you are. Aureal is accessible to everyone, everywhere.

--- Go Live:
With Aureal you can host your Live Streams, Rooms and invite people to join the discussions, you can re-stream this to other platforms like Twitch, Youtube Live etc. You can download and publish as a podcast and monetise.

--- Create without constraints:

Aureal is censorship resistant, if your opinions have been suppressed on other platforms and you feel that you weren't fairly treated, Aureal is a place for you.

Aureal is a decentralized app where your audience has absolute control. There is no central authority. It's a democratic social podcasting app the way it should be "Social".

--- Get Paid to Listen and Curate:

If you're just a listener, you get monetary curation rewards. Your interactions have value. Here you can

- Publish your podcast
- Start your podcast
- Upvote
- Comment
- Go Live
- Curate

Every interaction on Aureal gives you rewards.

--- Start earning in Bitcoin:
Aureal enables creators to earn in satoshis, the unitary form of Bitcoin whenever a listener consumes content.

The pain of searching for ads or sponsorships ends here.


Download the free app to monetise your content from day one with a click of a button. Earn the value for your efforts, time and voice because,

Your voice is worth something.

Welcome to Web 3.0 and Podcasting 2.0
descriptionShort: Social podcasting for Web 3.0
